<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Oral Medicine Residency Hub</title>
    <!-- Reverted to the universally stable CDN link to prevent local browser rendering blocks -->
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-white text-slate-900 font-sans">

    <nav class="bg-white shadow-md sticky top-0 z-50">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="flex justify-between h-16">
                <div class="flex items-center">
                    <span class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-950 tracking-tight">Oral Medicine Hub</span>
                </div>
                <div class="hidden md:flex items-center space-x-8">
                    <a href="#about" class="text-slate-700 hover:text-red-700 transition">About Us</a>
                    <a href="#clinical" class="text-slate-700 hover:text-red-700 transition">Clinical Sites</a>
                    <a href="#news" class="text-slate-700 hover:text-red-700 transition">News & Blog</a>
                    <a href="#contact" class="text-slate-700 hover:text-red-700 transition">Contact</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <header class="bg-gradient-to-br from-red-800 to-red-950 text-white py-24 px-4 text-center">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-6">Oral Medicine Residency Program</h1>
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-100 mb-8">An independent educational and clinical showcase managed by the residency team.</p>
            <a href="#about" class="bg-white hover:bg-red-50 text-red-800 font-bold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg transition shadow-md">Meet the Team</a>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section id="about" class="py-20 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-red-900">Academic Leadership</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-600 mt-2">Expert faculty guiding the next generation of specialists.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-16">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-red-800 mb-6 border-b-2 border-red-100 pb-2">Program Directors</h3>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-red-50">
                    <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-950">Dr. Firoozeh Samim</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm text-red-700 font-medium mb-2">Program Director, Oral Pathologist & Oral Medicine Specialist</p>
                    <p class="text-slate-700 text-sm">A leading clinician specializing in complex oral pathologies, mucosal diseases, and advanced diagnostics.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-red-50">
                    <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-950">Dr. Gilles Lavigne</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm text-red-700 font-medium mb-2">Program Director</p>
                    <p class="text-slate-700 text-sm">International expert specializing in orofacial pain management, sleep medicine, and clinical research methodologies.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-16">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-red-800 mb-6 border-b-2 border-red-100 pb-2">Second Year Residents (R2)</h3>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100">
                    <h4 class="text-base font-bold text-slate-950">Dr. Aia Naksho</h4>
                    <p class="text-xs text-red-700 mb-2">Senior Resident</p>
                    <p class="text-slate-700 text-sm">Managing complex outpatient care plans and advanced clinical workflows within institutional rotations.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100">
                    <h4 class="text-base font-bold text-slate-950">Dr. Zaneta Ivy D'Souza</h4>
                    <p class="text-xs text-red-700 mb-2">Senior Resident</p>
                    <p class="text-slate-700 text-sm">Focusing on multidisciplinary clinical protocols and diagnostic excellence in oral pathology.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-red-800 mb-6 border-b-2 border-red-100 pb-2">First Year Residents (R1)</h3>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                <div class="bg-white p-5 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100">
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-950">Dr. Bahy Shaheen Ahmed</h4>
                    <p class="text-xs text-red-700 mb-2">Resident & Web Administrator</p>
                    <p class="text-slate-700 text-sm">Interested in combining clinical diagnostics with modern digital technology to optimize communication.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white p-5 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100">
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-950">Dr. Elahe Akbari</h4>
                    <p class="text-xs text-red-700 mb-2">Resident</p>
                    <p class="text-slate-700 text-sm">Committed to clinical service excellence and patient centered dental medicine workflows.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white p-5 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100">
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-950">Dr. Carlos Santana Carlot</h4>
                    <p class="text-xs text-red-700 mb-2">Resident</p>
                    <p class="text-slate-700 text-sm">Exploring collaborative academic medicine networks and comprehensive patient care protocols.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="clinical" class="py-20 bg-slate-50">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="mb-12 text-center">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-red-950">Clinical Training Sites</h2>
                <p class="text-slate-600 mt-2">Our residency cohort actively rotates through premier healthcare centers.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-950 mb-2">Montreal General Hospital</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-700 text-sm">Providing comprehensive consultations for complex oral mucosal diseases, salivary gland disorders, and chronic orofacial pain.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-950 mb-2">McGill University Health Centre</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-700 text-sm">Integrating advanced clinical training with collaborative multidisciplinary medical and surgical teams.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="news" class="py-20 bg-white">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="mb-12">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-red-950">Residency News & Insights</h2>
                <p class="text-slate-600 mt-2">Updates on team clinical observations and program initiatives.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                <article class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100">
                    <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-red-700 tracking-wider uppercase">Program Update</span>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-950 mt-2 mb-3">Independent Digital Hub Online</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-4">We have launched our independent platform to enhance collaboration, streamline news distribution, and connect with peers globally.</p>
                    <span class="text-xs text-slate-400">June 2026</span>
                </article>
                <article class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100">
                    <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-red-700 tracking-wider uppercase">Clinical Focus</span>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-950 mt-2 mb-3">Welcoming the Incoming Cohort</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-4">Our first year residents have officially joined the rotation schedule across our core hospital affiliations.</p>
                    <span class="text-xs text-slate-400">June 2026</span>
                </article>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="contact" class="py-20 max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-red-950">Connect with Us</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-600 mt-2">Inquiries regarding academic updates or independent clinical collaborations are welcome.</p>
        </div>
        <form class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 space-y-6">
            <div>
                <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Name</label>
                <input type="text" class="w-full border border-slate-300 rounded-lg p-2.5 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red-500/20 focus:border-red-600" placeholder="Dr. Jane Doe">
            </div>
            <div>
                <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Email Address</label>
                <input type="email" class="w-full border border-slate-300 rounded-lg p-2.5 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red-500/20 focus:border-red-600" placeholder="jane.doe@example.com">
            </div>
            <div>
                <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Inquiry</label>
                <textarea rows="4" class="w-full border border-slate-300 rounded-lg p-2.5 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red-500/20 focus:border-red-600" placeholder="How can our team assist you?"></textarea>
            </div>
            <button type="button" class="w-full bg-red-900 hover:bg-red-800 text-white font-semibold py-3 rounded-lg transition shadow-md">Send Message</button>
        </form>
    </section>

    <footer class="bg-red-950 text-slate-200 py-8 text-center text-xs border-t border-red-900">
        <p>&copy; 2026 Oral Medicine Residency Team. This site runs independently of McGill University.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
